Name: Infinity Square
About the game: A game that no one has cleared yet! A game that even the father of the developer couldn't clear! Infinity Square is Casual Puzzle Game. Turn tiles and connect lines to clear the puzzles! You can find 2X2, 2X3, 3X3 puzzles! It has 8 chapters to play! It added more 4 difficulties to play. You can join it to clear last stage and click the tile on the main menu.
